      "type": "text",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 655,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "DApp/  (Vanilla HTML + jQuery)\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n  SimpleVoting.html\n  ├── Vote buttons → voteForCandidate()\n  └── Live vote count display\n\n  EtherTransfer.html\n  └── ETH transfer via web3.eth\n\n  ERC20Transfer.html\n  └── Token transfer via contract.methods\n\n  ERC20Optimism.html\n  └── L2 Optimism token interaction\n\n  Katinrun.html\n  └── Custom contract UI\n\n  web3.js  (bundled library ~1.5MB)",
