      "type": "text",
      "x": 505,
      "y": 1025,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "Nodejs/Expressjs/  (REST API Server)\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n  index.js  (Express server)\n  ├── Connects to Kovan via Infura\n  ├── Loads Bank contract ABI\n  │\n  ├── GET /systemBalance\n  ├── POST /deposit\n  └── POST /withdraw\n\n  Tech: express · web3 · cors\n  Pattern: REST → Contract → Blockchain",
